<h2 id="anova-table">ANOVA Table</h2>

<h3 id="two-factor-factorial-a-levels-of-a-b-levels-of-b-r-replicates">Two-Factor Factorial ($a$ levels of A, $b$ levels of B, $r$ replicates)</h3>

<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>Source</th>
      <th>df</th>
      <th>SS</th>
      <th>MS</th>
      <th>F</th>
    </tr>
