<h3 id="step-5--exploratory-data-analysis">Step 5 — Exploratory Data Analysis</h3>

<div class="language-r highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c1"># ── Treatment means ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="n">trt_summary</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">&lt;-</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">field_book</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">|&gt;</span><span class="w">
