<h3 id="step-16--non-parametric-alternative-friedman-test">Step 16 — Non-Parametric Alternative (Friedman Test)</h3>

<p>When normality or additivity assumptions fail:</p>

<div class="language-r highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c1"># ── Friedman test (non-parametric RCBD) ──────────────────────────────────</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="c1"># Requires wide format: rows = blocks, cols = treatments</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="n">wide_df</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">&lt;-</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">field_book</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">|&gt;</span><span class="w">
  </span><span class="n">select</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">trt</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">Block</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">Yield</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">|&gt;</span><span class="w">
  </span><span class="n">pivot_wider</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">names_from</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">trt</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">values_from</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">Yield</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w">

</span><span class="n">yield_mat</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">&lt;-</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">as.matrix</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">wide_df</span><span class="p">[,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="m">-1</span><span class="p">])</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="n">friedman.test</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">yield_mat</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w">

</span><span class="c1"># ── Post-hoc: Nemenyi test ────────────────────────────────────────────────</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">!</span><span class="n">requireNamespace</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">"PMCMRplus"</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">quietly</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">TRUE</span><span class="p">))</span><span class="w">
  </span><span class="n">install.packages</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">"PMCMRplus"</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="n">library</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">PMCMRplus</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="n">frdAllPairsNemenyiTest</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">yield_mat</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w">
</span></code></pre></div></div>

